// var =[]133,'Supplication said to the debtor when his debt is settled','De celui qui s''acquitte de ses dettes en faveur de celui qui lui a accordé','قرض کی ادائیگی کے وقت دعا','Qarz ki adaaigi ke waqt dua','Reference: An-Nasa''i,     ''Amalul-Yawm wal-Laylahp. 300, Ibn Majah 2/809. See also Al-Albani,     Sahih Ibn Majah2/55.','Reference: An-Nasa''i,     ''Amalul-Yawm wal-Laylahp. 300, Ibn Majah 2/809. See also Al-Albani,     Sahih Ibn Majah2/55.','ان۔نصآی ، عمل ۔ یوم ول۔ لےلھپ ۔ 300 ، ابن مجھ 2/ 809 ۔ آل۔ البانی ، صحیح ابن ماجہ 2/ 55 ۔','Reference: An-Nasa''i,     ''Amalul-Yawm wal-Laylahp. 300, Ibn Majah 2/809. See also Al-Albani,     Sahih Ibn Majah2/55.',1,'239');
// var =[]134,'Supplication for fear of shirk','Lorsque l''on craint le polythéisme (ach-Chirk)','شرک سے خوف کی دعا','Shirk se mehfooz rehne ki dua','Reference: Ahmad     4/403. See also Al-Albani, Sahihul-Jami'' As-Saghir 3/233 and     Sahihut-Targhib wat- Tarhib 1/19.','Reference: Ahmad     4/403. See also Al-Albani, Sahihul-Jami'' As-Saghir 3/233 and     Sahihut-Targhib wat- Tarhib 1/19.','آحمد 4/ 403، آل۔ البانی ، صحیح ال جمی اس۔ سگھڑ 3/ 233 اور صحیح ال ۔ترغیب وت۔ترغیب 1/ 19۔','Reference: Ahmad     4/403. See also Al-Albani, Sahihul-Jami'' As-Saghir 3/233 and     Sahihut-Targhib wat- Tarhib 1/19.',1,'240');
