// var =[]174,'To ward off the deception of the obstinate Shaytaans','Pour écarter la ruse et le complot des diables rebelles','سرکش شیاطین کے مکر و فریب سے بچنے کی دعائیں','Sarkash shyaateen ke makr o fareb se bachney ki dua','Reference: Ahmad     3/419, with an authentic chain of narration, and Ibn As-Sunni (no. 637).     Al-Arna''ut, graded its chain authentic in his checking of Al-''Aqidah At-Tahawiyyah     p. 133. See also Majma''uz-Zawa''id, 10/127.','Reference: Ahmad     3/419, with an authentic chain of narration, and Ibn As-Sunni (no. 637).     Al-Arna''ut, graded its chain authentic in his checking of Al-''Aqidah At-Tahawiyyah     p. 133. See also Majma''uz-Zawa''id, 10/127.','احمد 3/419 ، مستند سلسلہ حکایت کے ساتھ ، اور ابن آس-سنی (نمبر: 637)۔ العرناوت نے ، الاکیڈا عط طحاویہ صفحہ 133 کی جانچ پڑتال میں اس کی زنجیر کو مستند کیا۔ ماجماعزواضعید ، 10/127 بھی دیکھیں۔','Reference: Ahmad     3/419, with an authentic chain of narration, and Ibn As-Sunni (no. 637).     Al-Arna''ut, graded its chain authentic in his checking of Al-''Aqidah At-Tahawiyyah     p. 133. See also Majma''uz-Zawa''id, 10/127.',1,'294');
// var =[]175,'Seeking forgiveness and repentance','La demande d''absolution et le repentir','توبہ اور استغفار','Tauba o istighfaar','References: Abu Dawud 2/85, At-Tirmithi 5/569, and Al-Hakim who declared it authentic and Ath-Thahabi agreed with him 1/511. Al-Albani graded it authentic in Sahih At-Tirmithi 3/182. See also Jami''ul-''Usool li-''Ahdaith Ar-Rasool 4/ 389-90 checked by Al-Arna''ut.<br>At-Tirmithi, An-Nasa''i 1/279 and Al-Hakim. See also Al-Albani, Sahih At-Tirmithi 3/183, and Jdmi''ul-''Usool with Al-Arna''ut''s checking 4/144. <br>Muslim 1/350. <br>Muslim 4/2075','References: Abu Dawud 2/85, At-Tirmithi 5/569, and Al-Hakim who declared it authentic and Ath-Thahabi agreed with him 1/511. Al-Albani graded it authentic in Sahih At-Tirmithi 3/182. See also Jami''ul-''Usool li-''Ahdaith Ar-Rasool 4/ 389-90 checked by Al-Arna''ut.<br>At-Tirmithi, An-Nasa''i 1/279 and Al-Hakim. See also Al-Albani, Sahih At-Tirmithi 3/183, and Jdmi''ul-''Usool with Al-Arna''ut''s checking 4/144. <br>Muslim 1/350. <br>Muslim 4/2075','ابوداؤد 2/85 ، ترمذی 5/569 ، اور الحکیم جس نے اسے مستند قرار دیا اور اتثابی نے اس سے 1/511 پر اتفاق کیا۔ البانی نے صحیح ترمذی 3/182 میں اسے مستند درجہ دیا۔ جامع ''العسول لی-احدیت Ar الرسول 4 / 389-90 بھی ار checkedناوت کے ذریعہ چیک کردہ ملاحظہ کریں۔ <br> ترمذی ، عن نسائی 1/279 اور الحکیم۔ البانیہ ، صحیح الترمتھی 3/183 ، اور جدیمی العثول ال ارناوت کی جانچ پڑتال کے ساتھ 4/144 بھی ملاحظہ کریں۔ <br> مسلم 1/350۔ <br> مسلم 4/2075','References: Abu Dawud 2/85, At-Tirmithi 5/569, and Al-Hakim who declared it authentic and Ath-Thahabi agreed with him 1/511. Al-Albani graded it authentic in Sahih At-Tirmithi 3/182. See also Jami''ul-''Usool li-''Ahdaith Ar-Rasool 4/ 389-90 checked by Al-Arna''ut.<br>At-Tirmithi, An-Nasa''i 1/279 and Al-Hakim. See also Al-Albani, Sahih At-Tirmithi 3/183, and Jdmi''ul-''Usool with Al-Arna''ut''s checking 4/144. <br>Muslim 1/350. <br>Muslim 4/2075',1,'295,296');
// var =[]176,'Remembrance and glorification of Allaah','Les mérites de dire ''gloire à Allah, louange à Allah, il n''y a de divinité qu''Allah, Allah est le plus Grand''','تکبیر، تسبیح، تحمید، اور تحلیل کی فضیلت','Hamd o sana, takbir aur laa ilaaha illallaah ki fazeelat','[1] Al-Bukhari     7/168, Muslim 4/2071<br>[2] Al-Bukhari     7/67, Muslim 4/2071, see also invocation no. 93 of this book.<br>[3] Muslim     4/2072.<br>[4] Muslim     3/1685.<br>[5] Ahmad (no.     513) (Ahmad Shakir, ed.) and its chain of narration is authentic. See     Majma''uz-Zawa''id 1/297. Ibn Hajar mentions it in Bulughul-Maram saying     that Ibn Hibban and Al-Hakim considered it authentic.','[1] Al-Bukhari     7/168, Muslim 4/2071<br>[2] Al-Bukhari     7/67, Muslim 4/2071, see also invocation no. 93 of this book.<br>[3] Muslim     4/2072.<br>[4] Muslim     3/1685.<br>[5] Ahmad (no.     513) (Ahmad Shakir, ed.) and its chain of narration is authentic. See     Majma''uz-Zawa''id 1/297. Ibn Hajar mentions it in Bulughul-Maram saying     that Ibn Hibban and Al-Hakim considered it authentic.','[1] البخاری 7/168 ، مسلم 4/2071 <br> [2] البخاری 7/67 ، مسلم 4/2071 ، یہ بھی ملاحظہ کریں۔ اس کتاب کا 93۔ <br> [3] مسلم 4/2072۔ <br> [4] مسلم 3/1685۔ <br> روایت مستند ہے۔ ملاحظہ الزوائد 1/297 دیکھیں۔ ابن حجر نے بلغول مرام میں اس کا تذکرہ کرتے ہوئے کہا ہے کہ ابن حبان اور الحکیم اس کو مستند سمجھتے ہیں۔','[1] Al-Bukhari     7/168, Muslim 4/2071<br>[2] Al-Bukhari     7/67, Muslim 4/2071, see also invocation no. 93 of this book.<br>[3] Muslim     4/2072.<br>[4] Muslim     3/1685.<br>[5] Ahmad (no.     513) (Ahmad Shakir, ed.) and its chain of narration is authentic. See     Majma''uz-Zawa''id 1/297. Ibn Hajar mentions it in Bulughul-Maram saying     that Ibn Hibban and Al-Hakim considered it authentic.',1,'297,298,299,300,301,302,303,304,305,306,307,308,309');
