// var =[278,'Duas to be said when fearing injustice or attack from authority / ruler','Dua to be said when fearing injustice or attack from authority / ruler','دشمن سے نجات','Dua for protection from enemy #1',replace('[1] ''Abdullah ibn Mas''ud said, "When there is a ruler in charge of you whose arrogance or injustice is feared, you should say, [this dua] [Ref: Al-Bukhari, Al-''Adab Al-Mufrad (no. 707). Al-Albani graded it authentic in Sahih Al-''Adab Al-Mufrad (no. 545).]<br><br>[2] Ibn ''Abbas said, "When you go to an awesome ruler and fear that he will attack you, say, [this dua] three times. [Ref: Al-Bukhari, Al-''Adab Al-Mufrad (no. 708). Al-Albani graded it authentic in Sahih Al-''Adab\n￼Al-Mufrad (no. 546).]','\n',char(10)),replace('[1] ''Abdullah ibn Mas''ud said, "When there is a ruler in charge of you whose arrogance or injustice is feared, you should say, [this dua] [Ref: Al-Bukhari, Al-''Adab Al-Mufrad (no. 707). Al-Albani graded it authentic in Sahih Al-''Adab Al-Mufrad (no. 545).]<br><br>[2] Ibn ''Abbas said, "When you go to an awesome ruler and fear that he will attack you, say, [this dua] three times. [Ref: Al-Bukhari, Al-''Adab Al-Mufrad (no. 708). Al-Albani graded it authentic in Sahih Al-''Adab\n￼Al-Mufrad (no. 546).]','\n',char(10)),'[1] ''عبد اللہ ابن مسعود نے کہا ، "جب آپ پر کوئی حکمران ایسا ہو جس کے تکبر یا ناانصافی کا اندیشہ ہو تو آپ کو یہ کہنا چاہئے ، [اس دعا] [حوالہ: البخاری ، الاعداب المفراد (نمبر 707)۔ البانی رحم اللہ علیہ نے صحیح العابد المفراد (نمبر: 545) میں اسے مستند قرار دیا۔] <br> <br> [2] ابن عباس نے کہا ، "جب آپ کسی حیرت انگیز حکمران کے پاس جاتے ہیں اور ڈرو کہ وہ تم پر حملہ کرے گا ، کہو ، [اس دعا] نے تین بار۔ [حوالہ: البخاری ، الاعداب المفراد (نمبر: 708) البانی نے صحیح العباد میں مستند درجہ دیا الفرض (نمبر: 546)۔]',replace('[1] ''Abdullah ibn Mas''ud said, "When there is a ruler in charge of you whose arrogance or injustice is feared, you should say, [this dua] [Ref: Al-Bukhari, Al-''Adab Al-Mufrad (no. 707). Al-Albani graded it authentic in Sahih Al-''Adab Al-Mufrad (no. 545).]<br><br>[2] Ibn ''Abbas said, "When you go to an awesome ruler and fear that he will attack you, say, [this dua] three times. [Ref: Al-Bukhari, Al-''Adab Al-Mufrad (no. 708). Al-Albani graded it authentic in Sahih Al-''Adab\n￼Al-Mufrad (no. 546).]','\n',char(10)),0,'412,413');
