      'Allah taala ke naam se (shuru) jo nihayat meharban, bahot rahem karne wala hai {Aap keh dijiye! ke mein logon ke Rab ki panah mein aata hun, logon ke badshah ki, logon ke mabood ki, waswasa daalnay walay shaytan se jo aankhon se oojhal hai, jo logon ke seenon mein waswasa dalta hai,jino mein se aur insanon meinse}',
