      'Ae Allah! Tu hi mera Rab hai tairay siwa koi mabood nahi Tu ne mujhe paida farmaya, aur mein tera bandah hun aur mein apni taaqat ke mutabiq tairay ahed aur waday par qaim hun mein tujh se us cheez ke shar se panah mangta hun jis ka mein ne irtikaab kiya, mein tairay samnay tairay inaam ka iqraar karta hun jo mujh par huwa aur mein apne gunaaho ka iqraar karta hun, lehaza Tu mujhe maaf kardey. waqea yeh hai ke tairay siwa koi gunaaho ko maaf nahi karsaktha ',
