  duaitems(
      160,
      'اللّهُـمَّ رَحْمَتَـكَ أَرْجـوفَلا تَكِلـني إِلى نَفْـسي طَـرْفَةَ عَـيْن، وَأَصْلِـحْ لي شَأْنـي كُلَّـه لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا أنْـت',
      'aud035_2',
      'img035_2',
      'Allaahumma rahmataka '
          'arjoo falaa takilnee '
          'ilaa nafsee tarfata '
          'aynin, wa '
          'aslih lee sha'
          'nee kullahu, laa'
          'ilaaha '
          'illaa '
          'Anta.',
      'O Allah , I hope for Your mercy . Do not leave me to myself even for the blinking of an eye (i.e. a moment) . Correct all of my affairs for me . There is none worthy of worship but You.[2].',
